      • deserialize

        public T deserialize(byte[] messageKey,
                     byte[] message,
                     java.lang.String topic,
                     int partition,
                     long offset)
              throws java.io.IOException
        从接口复制的说明: KeyedDeserializationSchema
        Deserializes the byte message.
        指定者:
        deserialize 在接口中 KeyedDeserializationSchema<T>
        参数:
        messageKey - the key as a byte array (null if no key has been set).
        message - The message, as a byte array (null if the message was empty or deleted).
        partition - The partition the message has originated from.
        offset - the offset of the message in the original source (for example the Kafka offset).
        返回:
        The deserialized message as an object (null if the message cannot be deserialized).
        抛出:
        java.io.IOException

      • isEndOfStream

        public boolean isEndOfStream(T nextElement)
        从接口复制的说明: KeyedDeserializationSchema
        Method to decide whether the element signals the end of the stream. If true is returned the element won't be emitted.
        指定者:
        isEndOfStream 在接口中 KeyedDeserializationSchema<T>
        参数:
        nextElement - The element to test for the end-of-stream signal.
        返回:
        True, if the element signals end of stream, false otherwise.
